text: Dell Rapids is a city in the eastern part of the U.S. state of South Dakota. It is in Minnehaha County, about twenty miles north of Sioux Falls, the largest city in South Dakota. It became a city in 1888, and 3,996 people lived there at the 2020 census. == References == == Other websites == *City of Dell Rapids website Category:Cities in South Dakota Category:1888 establishments in the United States Category:1880s establishments in Dakota Territory
